    @Name(value="nd4j::ops::sequence_mask<float>")
public static class Nd4jCpu.float_sequence_mask
extends Nd4jCpu.FloatDeclarableCustomOp
    sequence_mask op. - make mask for given tensor filled by (j > x[i_1, i_2,...,i_n]) -> z[i_1, i_2,...,i_n,j] input params: 0 - the ND-tensor filled by integer-like values optional int param - maxlength (maxlength >= max(x)). By default maxlength = max(x). return value: (N+1)D tensor filled by 0 and 1 accordingly the mask
